Package: cRypto
Type: Package
Title: cRypto: Pull cryptocurrency data in tidy format form coinmarketcap API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Adelmo", "Filho", email = "adelmo.aguiar.filho@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A wrapper for pulling cryptocurrency data in tidy format form coinmarketcap API. By automatically batching API requests, it allows you to enter an cryptocurrency's name and retrieve their historical or today data.
URL: https://https://github.com/adelmofilho/cRypto
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), dplyr
Imports: purrr, httr
Suggests: testthat
